Name: netlink-packet-core
URL: https://github.com/rust-netlink/netlink-packet-core
Version: 0.7.0
Security Critical: yes

License File: LICENSE-MIT
  License: MIT

Description:
  This crate provides the core functionality for serialization/deserialization of
  NETLINK messages. It is used by Starnix to serve the NETLINK protocol.

  This crate forks upstream version 0.7.0. There are several divergences from
  upstream (See the git history for the complete list). At this point, there is
  no intention of re-merging with upstream.
